(15, 3, 'SOFER PERSONAL', '                    <p><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Pentru confortul dvs, va oferim posibilitatea inchirierii unui sofer personal alaturi de autoturismul ales.</span><br style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Soferul va va sta la dispozitie pe perioada dorita.</span><br style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Pentru detalii, va rugam consultati&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.rent-a-car-timisoara.com/servicii-speciale.html" target="_blank" style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; color: rgb(7, 147, 200); text-decoration: none;">pagina</a><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px;">&nbsp;</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px;">dedicata.</span></p><p style="text-align: right;"><a href="http://www.rent-a-car-timisoara.com/servicii-speciale.html" target="_blank" style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12px; word-spacing: 4px;">CITESTE MAI MULT</a></p>                ', 'no'),
(16, 3, 'TRACTARI AUTO', '                                        <p><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Compania noastra va ofera asistenta tehnica si tractare in cazul unui accident sau a unei defectiuni care va pune in imposibilitatea de a va continua drumul.</span><br style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Echipa noastra pentru cazurile de avarie va reactiona prompt si va va asista cu profesionalism.</span><br style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Acest serviciu este diponibil NON STOP.</span><br style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Pentru detalii, va rugam consultati&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.rent-a-car-timisoara.com/servicii-speciale.html" target="_blank" style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; color: rgb(7, 147, 200); text-decoration: none;">pagina</a><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px;">&nbsp;</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px;">dedicata.</span></p><p style="text-align: right;"><a href="http://www.rent-a-car-timisoara.com/servicii-speciale.html" target="_blank" style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12px; word-spacing: 4px;">CITESTE MAI MULT</a></p>                                ', 'no'),
(17, 3, 'LEASING OPERATIONAL', '                    <p><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Agar Company va ofera servicii de inchirieri autoturisme pe termen lung ( in sistem de Leasing Operational cu servicii incluse).</span><br style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Parcul auto este compus din autoturisme noi, intretinute conform prescriptiilor producÄƒtorilor, astfel, prin serviciul de leasing, autoturismul de care veti beneficia este in cea mai buna stare de functionare si conform normelor de siguranta.</span><br style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Pentru detalii, va rugam consultati&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.rent-a-car-timisoara.com/operational-leasing.html" target="_blank" style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; color: rgb(7, 147, 200); text-decoration: none;">pagina</a><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px;">&nbsp;</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px;">dedicata.</span></p><p style="text-align: right;"><a href="http://www.rent-a-car-timisoara.com/operational-leasing.html" target="_blank" style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12px; word-spacing: 4px;">CITESTE MAI MULT</a></p>                ', 'no'),
(18, 4, 'VANZARI AUTOTURISME', '                    <span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">AGAR COMPANY detine un parc auto cu o diversitate de autoturisme, de la cele de fiecare zi, pana la autoturisme de lux si utilitare.</span><br style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Compania selecteaza cu atentie autoturismele ce urmeaza sa fie puse in vanzare si prin asta va ofera o varietate de marci si modele la standarde inatlte.</span><br style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">AGAR COMPANY va asigura un istoric detaliat al autoturismelor, iar dvs puteti fi siguri ca veti avea un autoturism la un pret foarte bun si o sursa de incredere.</span><br style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Pentru detalii, va rugam consultati </span><div class="text_link" style="clear: none; display: inline; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><a href="http://agarcars.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(7, 147, 200);">pagina</a></div><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> dedicata.</span><div style="text-align: right;"><br class="Apple-interchange-newline"><span style="color: rgb(7, 147, 200); font-family: helvetica; font-size: 9px; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><a href="h