(19, 5, 'INCHIRIERI', '                    <span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">AGAR Company APARTHOTEL va pune la dispozitie apartamente in zona centrala a orasului, la standarde inalte de confort si utilate ultra modern.</span><br style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Ideale pentru cazare pe timpul calatoriilor de afaceri, de weekend, de vacanta, apartamentele noastre sunt cea mai buna alternativa a hotelurilor, oferindu-va conditii excelente si, in acelasi timp, intimitatea propriului camin.</span><br style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Pentru detalii, va rugam consultati </span><div class="text_link" style="clear: none; display: inline; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><a href="http://rentintm.com/rezervare.html" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(7, 147, 200);">pagina</a></div><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> dedicata.</span><div style="text-align: right;"><br class="Apple-interchange-newline"><span style="color: rgb(7, 147, 200); font-family: helvetica; font-size: 9px; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; word-spacing: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><a href="http://rentintm.com/rezervare.html" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(7, 147, 200);">CITESTE MAI MULT</a></span></div>                ', 'no'),
